{"tid":1212922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[BeWater]有突發情況 塞地鐵人士請留意！","createTime":"2019-06-12T23:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T09:30:15.000Z","uid":87858,"like":297,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"7dc083d77fbab595269992a30cb44ff1bac85f3f","tid":1212922,"uid":87858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:32:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大膽去立會，細膽停鐵，留港島荃灣線去立會<br />\n有gp730行動</span></span><br />\n<br />\n613 好戲之人, 唔舒服都起身番工<br />\n1. 目標 : 長時間令該線行唔到，做到癱瘓港鐵，迫令全人類罷工罷課罷市。 <br />\n2.總站一次過上車,安全，集體行動<br />\n3. 中間車卡上車，最快做到塞的效果<br />\n4.如有差人來 (一定有，因為大谷有狗 ),我地做戲做全套。話唔舒服就得，千奇唔好有衝突，記得有禮貌！<br />\n5. 塞繁忙線為佳。如果塞山卡啦線，塞來托？<br />\n6.時間 : 繁忙時間為佳 ，8點開始<br />\n7. 宗旨 ：a. 封經濟 b.保護支援路線 c. 帶出塞地鐵訊息俾身邊人，確保足夠人玩<br />\n<br />\n叫勿塞者，必踢. 有問題，搵 admin<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/saveHK613\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FsaveHK613&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMfkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=d729750a\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/saveHK613</a><br />\n<br />\n轉至計劃移民巴"},{"pid":"38b206def76f9d7a76fd3044d5be66e185746717","tid":1212922,"uid":87858,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:34:06.000Z","msg":"呢個時候各有各做喇<br />\n唔好花時間拗<br />\n主要係唔好互相阻左大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7407294e9d081700361e90e52e1abe33258bad","tid":1212922,"uid":87858,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:35:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04c75ed9c7a40caeed49634a3440f34cb52af2a2","tid":1212922,"uid":87858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:35:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e9872621f728ffff5dda6889ee63e831e91e56d","tid":1212922,"uid":159307,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:36:55.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好亂拋垃圾落路軌"},{"pid":"0d9c941723a262e29790961eff86b9902edf96af","tid":1212922,"uid":87858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"